Email notification of watched pages will always contain the *content* of the page and a summary of what has been changed

*Suggestion*
 It will be nice if there is an option to choose whether users would like to have:
 * Contents of the watched pages included;
 * No content. The email would be just a "Notification" of which pages that has been edited/changed;
 * No email triggered - only the notification on the app;
 * Specify which changes should trigger the email notification (only when comment is deleted on a page, only when content is added, etc).

*Scenarios:*
 * Prevent sending content snippets of private information via the email to our external partners.

